  <title>Problem with Audio CD</title>

  <p>
    Please notice, that <app>Videos</app> does not support playback of Audio CDs.
    You may use other music player, or rip your Audio CD and then play it in
    <app>Videos</app>. <app>Sound Juicer</app> may be used to rip your Audio CD.
  </p>
  <terms>
    <item>
      <title><code>Ripping CD</code></title>
